.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
City: edinburgh, new-york, london, venice
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the social-worker is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| City          | edinburgh | london  | venice    | new-york       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 